{"word":"G3656 - ὁμιλέω - homiléō - hom-il-eh'-o - Commune","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁμιλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">homiléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hom-il-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Commune</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பேசிக்கொள், பேசு"},{"paragraph":"to be in company with; to associate with; to stay with; to converse with, talk with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3658 - ὅμιλος - hómilos - hom'-il-os/3658\">G3658</a>; to <i>be in company</i> with, that is, (by implication) to <i>converse:</i> - commune, talk.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3656/3656\">G3656</a>, <a href=\"#/G3657/3657\">G3657</a>, <a href=\"#/G3658/3658\">G3658</a>"}]}